node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kandi Burruss on September 06, 2021 tagging @cousinwennie. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Happy Birthday to my @cousinwennie! She’s the glue in our family that keeps us all connected & always checks on everybody. I love you so much & I pray you’re having an amazing bday!
